integrations.zendesk_description: Export your call intake to Zendesk
zendesk_long_description: Ensure that your Zendesk campaign reaches the intended target audience with AnswerForce. For every new customer created at AnswerForce, this integration will automatically add corresponding contact information to your Zendesk campaign list.
zendesk_instruction: Click the ‘Connect’ button on the right-hand side of this window.
Enter your Zendesk username and password to allow access to AnswerForce.
Confirm the action by clicking Allow. The integration will now be connected.
